## Notes

- Engine version `Autodesk.Revit+2024` — change `ENGINE_VERSION` env var to target 2025/2026
- All measurements are output in **metric** (m, m², converted from Revit's internal feet)
- Rooms with zero area (unplaced) are excluded
- Warnings are capped at 50 to keep the report lean
